title: Garmin City Navigator Europe NT 2014.10 Unlocked
description:
Unlocked complete map of Europe 2014.10 sliced into individual groups of countries and is ready to write to the device Garmin. Includes more than 10.4 million kilometers (6.5 million miles) of roads, including motorways, national and regional thoroughfares and local roads in Western Europe and many countries in Eastern Europe.

Displays more than 6 million points of interest throughout the region, including restaurants, lodging, border crossings, attractions, petrol stations, campsites, shopping.
Pronunciation of street names (eg "Turn right on Main Street").
Includes navigation features (routing).
Contains traffic data for compatible devices that use traffic receivers.
